========================
TAILWIND CSS CHEAT SHEET
========================

--------------------------------
1. LAYOUT & DISPLAY
--------------------------------
block            -> display: block
inline-block     -> display: inline-block
inline           -> display: inline
flex             -> display: flex
inline-flex      -> display: inline-flex
grid             -> display: grid
hidden           -> display: none

--------------------------------
2. FLEXBOX
--------------------------------
flex-row         -> flex-direction: row
flex-col         -> flex-direction: column
flex-row-reverse -> row-reverse
flex-col-reverse -> column-reverse

items-start      -> align-items: flex-start
items-center     -> align-items: center
items-end        -> align-items: flex-end
items-stretch    -> align-items: stretch

justify-start    -> justify-content: flex-start
justify-center   -> justify-content: center
justify-end      -> justify-content: flex-end
justify-between  -> space-between
justify-around   -> space-around
justify-evenly   -> space-evenly

gap-1..gap-96    -> gap between flex/grid items

flex-1           -> flex: 1
flex-none        -> flex: none
flex-wrap        -> flex-wrap
flex-nowrap      -> no wrap

--------------------------------
3. GRID
--------------------------------
grid-cols-1..12  -> number of columns
grid-rows-1..6   -> number of rows

col-span-1..12   -> span columns
row-span-1..6    -> span rows

place-items-center -> align + justify items center
place-content-center

--------------------------------
4. SPACING (PADDING & MARGIN)
--------------------------------
p-0..p-96        -> padding all sides
px-              -> padding left/right
py-              -> padding top/bottom
pt- pr- pb- pl-  -> padding specific side

m-0..m-96        -> margin all sides
mx-              -> margin left/right
my-              -> margin top/bottom
mt- mr- mb- ml-  -> margin specific side

-auto            -> auto margin (e.g mx-auto)

--------------------------------
5. WIDTH & HEIGHT
--------------------------------
w-0..w-96        -> fixed width
h-0..h-96        -> fixed height

w-full           -> 100%
h-full           -> 100%
w-screen         -> 100vw
h-screen         -> 100vh

min-w-0          -> min-width
min-h-0
max-w-sm/md/lg/xl/2xl/7xl
max-h-screen

--------------------------------
6. POSITIONING
--------------------------------
relative
absolute
fixed
sticky

top-0 right-0 bottom-0 left-0
inset-0          -> top/right/bottom/left 0

z-0 z-10 z-20 z-30 z-40 z-50

--------------------------------
7. TYPOGRAPHY
--------------------------------
text-xs sm base lg xl 2xl 3xl 4xl 5xl 6xl
font-thin light normal medium semibold bold extrabold

tracking-tight normal wide wider widest
leading-none tight normal relaxed loose

text-left center right justify
uppercase lowercase capitalize normal-case

--------------------------------
8. COLORS
--------------------------------
text-black white gray-100..900
bg-black white gray-100..900
border-black gray-200 etc

text-red blue green yellow purple pink
bg-red-500
border-blue-600

--------------------------------
9. BORDERS & RADIUS
--------------------------------
border           -> border 1px
border-0..4
border-t r b l

rounded-none sm md lg xl 2xl full

--------------------------------
10. BACKGROUNDS
--------------------------------
bg-cover
bg-contain
bg-center
bg-top bg-bottom
bg-no-repeat
bg-repeat

--------------------------------
11. EFFECTS
--------------------------------
shadow-sm md lg xl 2xl
shadow-none

opacity-0..100
blur-sm md lg xl
brightness-50..200

--------------------------------
12. TRANSFOR
